ns0:Concept.displayName: Gestational age Estimated from last menstrual period

ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent the estimated gestational age at delivery.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Assessment, Performed. The intent of this data element is to identify the fetus's estimated length of gestation at delivery.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with LOINC codes that identify the estimated gestational age at delivery.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
